export const Login = () => {
  return (
    <form>
      <label for="email">email</label>
      <input
        type="email"
        placeholder="example@gmail.com"
        id="email"
        name="email"
      />
      <label for="password">password</label>
      <input
        type="password"
        placeholder="*******"
        id="password"
        name="password"
      />
      <button ></button>
    </form>
  );
};
